tive elements have `data-testid` attributes per RULE-F10\n- Chip filter row uses `role=\"button\"` with keyboard support\n- Property cards are clickable with `role=\"button\"` and keyboard support\n- Search input + button form ready for navigation integration\n- \"How It Works\" nav link scrolls to the section via `document.getElementById`\n\n### Files Modified\n- `frontend/app/pages/landing.tsx` — Created\n- `frontend/public/locales/en/common.json` — Added `landing` i18n namespace\n- `frontend/public/locales/ko/common.json` — Added `landing` i18n namespace (Korean translations)\n","filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/FRONTEND_CONVERT_A-01-landing.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/FRONTEND_CONVERT_A-01-landing.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/status/FRONTEND_CONVERT_A-01-landing.md","time":{"start":1779193209217,"end":1779193209500}},"id":"prt_e402d81e9001tfqaGX9yTr2Znj","sessionID":"ses_1bfdeff9cffel20XYIHhGhKvJ3","messageID":"msg_e402babc3001nyuJGVqZPiIt9S"}}
